name: FNF - Vs. Omori Full Week
description:
"Welcome To White Space, you've been living here for as long as you can remember."

Boyfriend and Girlfriend have found themselves in a blank white void since they wanted a challenge. However, when they arrived in a certain boys dreams, they found themselves confronted by a strange black and white kid, named OMORI, and his pet cat. Boyfriend, of course, harasses the kid for a rap battle.
